Package: pubclassify
Title: Retrieve and Classify Bibliometric Publication Metadata
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Lucy", "Andrews", , "lucy.andrews@water.ca.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Retrieve peer-reviewed publication metadata from bibliometric
    APIs including OpenAlex, Scopus, and Crossref, with support for
    classifying publications into user-defined scholarly field taxonomies
    using large language models.
